{"tid":2181300,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"喜歡整Siri shortcut嘅你，有冇煩惱？","createTime":"2020-08-30T13:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T05:02:59.000Z","uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7e995e43615d852fdae1cd05238e8e370b427bb8","tid":2181300,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"真係會發覺原來有好多好想有嘅嘢係唔做得，求其數幾樣啦：<br />\n<br />\n1）影相唔識幫你禁埋掣，只識打開camera app，我覺得係怕保安問題，其實可以要求人講一個密碼先影囉<br />\n<br />\n2）冇screenshot同screen recording ，我明白呢兩個亦關乎保安，萬一個shortcut將啲私隱send咗出去點算，之但係share location同contact又得？我好想佢俾用家自己決定<br />\n<br />\n3）拍片竟然冇stop呢個action，冇得自己program個時限，要人手停錄<br />\n<br />\n4）automation得太少triggers，冇電池level，冇kill app，冇day of months，冇月尾，冇start/stop recording audio 或video，冇完成download，冇documents saved，最後係堆sensors嘅triggers<br />\n<br />\n5）有埋自動化控制埋vpn設定就一流<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係一個真正嘅app developers，我知呢堆嘢識寫apps係可以全部解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e649ac210de78f39eea650337bac5db6049de134","tid":2181300,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"第一個已經唔知你up乜<br />\n一路都有得自動影 成日玩啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvdRnL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvdRnL8.png&h=dad2c148&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"814c718e063ff227ad2744305903aafd6e17d0da","tid":2181300,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"e649ac210de78f39eea650337bac5db6049de134","tid":2181300,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"第一個已經唔知你up乜<br />\n一路都有得自動影 成日玩啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvdRnL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvdRnL8.png&h=dad2c148&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:36:57.000Z",